{"tid":2133973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭月娥：至少68個國家和地區押後選舉，只有49個如期舉行","createTime":"2020-07-31T11:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T13:57:44.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6500531343765f13ff2a131fa56d887993c9fd13","tid":2133973,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"她又援引國際組織數據，指截至7月15日，有62個國家及8個屬地，因應疫情押後選舉。另一組織數據亦稱，由2月21日至7月26日，至少68個國家和地區押後選舉，只有49個國家或地區如期舉行選舉。而英國和澳洲，也會各自押後選舉至2021年舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2711869/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A%E9%9C%80%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%87%B3%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%885%E6%97%A5%E3%80%80%E6%8C%87%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E9%9B%A3%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%9F%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2711869%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%2587%25B3%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B49%25E6%259C%25885%25E6%2597%25A5%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG12LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=1dced62d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2711869/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A%E9%9C%80%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%87%B3%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B49%E6%9C%885%E6%97%A5%E3%80%80%E6%8C%87%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E9%9B%A3%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%9F%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真普選，獨立調查就無你份啦<br />\n<br />\n爆眼呀，国安法呀，押後選舉就「人哋都係咁啦！」"},{"pid